  ## 3. **Protein Measurement Terms in efo-edit.owl**                         
                                                                              
  Yes, many protein measurement terms exist (30 lines shown):                 
                                                                              
  • **C-reactive protein measurement** (with synonym "C-reactive protein      
  level")                                                                     
  • **Albumin measurement** - quantification in blood                         
  • **Total blood protein measurement** - measures albumin and globulin       
  • **Glycoprotein measurement**                                              
  • **Protein C measurement** and **Protein S measurement**                   
  • **C4b-binding protein levels/measurement**                                
  • **Apolipoprotein A1/B measurement** (lipoproteins)                        
  • **IGFBP-3 measurement** (insulin-like growth factor binding protein)      
  • **Von Willebrand factor measurement**                                     
  • Multiple factor and growth factor measurements                            
                                                                              
